Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:06.44,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}麦わら帽子も　ラララ　脱げずにいたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:10.94,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}晩生な　a lonely maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:18.29,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}不思議な導き　潮の満ち引き
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:24.27,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}夢見るみたいに出会えたら　Ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.11,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}わたしはRomantic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:30.02,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}あなたもRomantic
