Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:18.29,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}有種不可思議的指引  潮起潮落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:24.27,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}引出了像做夢般的邂逅　Ah-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:27.11,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}我很羅曼蒂克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:30.02,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}你也很羅曼蒂克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.89,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}全世界都羅曼蒂克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.93,0:02:35.87,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}曬傷了也毫不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:37.83,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}Summer Summer Love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.77,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,150)}{\be1}我想下定決心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:20.33,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}そっと伸ばした　その手ひら　零れ落ちる夕日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:26.30,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}波の音が　強く優しく　風に泳いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:32.36,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}戻れない道　歩き出す　一歩一歩ずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:38.34,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}あなたの隣　微笑んでる　不安を隠して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:45.21,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}心に決めた　あの日からだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:50.27,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}耳鳴りのように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:55.39,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}囁きかけてくる　オレンジの空は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:23:02.17,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}遥かに遠く、近く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:07.92,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}囁きかけてくる　オレンジの海に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:17.04,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}私は明日への光　見つけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:20.33,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}在殘陽當中  你靜靜地伸出了手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:26.30,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}海浪的聲音  猛烈又溫柔  沐浴在風中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:32.36,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}一步一步地邁向不歸之路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:38.34,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}在你身旁微笑  掩飾著心中的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:45.21,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}就是從下定決心的那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:50.27,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}猶如耳鳴般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:55.39,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}那輕輕細語的橙色天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:23:02.17,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}是那麼的遙遠而又相近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:07.92,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}在那輕輕細語的橙色大海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:17.04,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}我找到了通往明日的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ha  ha  ha…爸爸在这
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小燦  我的小燦  我的宝贝女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把以前那个可爱的小燦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙  那家伙  那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙  那只从埼玉来的孑孓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小燦变得奇奇怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪个杀手能去灭了那色胚！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的话  是你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满潮永澄  南无阿弥陀佛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.19,0:01:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户所流淌的晚潮和小浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救的少年永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.41,0:01:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情理上过得去 但道理上却行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请开怀大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海蓝色的恋爱要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&\3c&Hffffff&\shad0}最接近天堂的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:03:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濑户内  夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  离别突然就到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要回埼玉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然就决定明天走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司打电话过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「十万火急  赶快回来」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是暑假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交货期要提前了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太专横独断了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是公司的一只细小齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄你要做一只大大的  出色的齿轮才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯  尽我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小燦那边你要亲口对她说哦  没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好对她说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说  要怎么开口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  能看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政先生～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里就是目的地无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  今天要去那里玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过真的很意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原先极力反对我们结婚的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然叫我们两个到无人岛去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还派船来送
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  不可思议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  燦小姐的父亲也承认了两位的关系了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.24,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷贝小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会做两位的电灯泡的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么快就和永澄搞好关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是小燦的朋友  卷贝小卷吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  海洋生物这样子行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄先生一直盯着我的说  好害羞的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷还真爱害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  那个岳父大人竟然会承认我们的关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得美啊  海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幻听了…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉了要掉了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么两位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我傍晚再回来迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  政先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多小心注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那个  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个脚印都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把整个岛包下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心被谋杀  终于可以放心玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很漂亮吧  永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是个乐园啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  热  好热
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧  小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄  我们把行李放到树荫下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小卷也好好抓紧我  别被晒伤咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随随便便碰我  你这海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜  你以为我被区区海浪卷走就会出事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是海洋生物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我说「不要紧吧  小卷」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竖起耳朵给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是濑户内组保镖兼杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓到连孩子都不敢哭的卷贝阿卷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.72,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷贝的卷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷  是刺客！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫就是一海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多年来守护着小姐不让害虫靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这杀千刀的海蟑螂还出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家世世代代都侍奉着小姐她家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐竟然把像我这样身份的人当朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能把小姐交给你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被扎死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄  小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来游泳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  燦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙的态度还因人而异
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  什么时候跑到地面上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能活着离开这个岛就好了  永澄先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燦小姐要游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:51.79,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于派出专业杀手了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄也快点换衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  小燦的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别色迷迷地盯着看  杀千刀的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  我怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也跟小燦她老爸生死搏斗过存活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以输呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小不点根本不是对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰飞至渣吧  臭蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}liquid machine-gun{\r}\N水铁炮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰飞至渣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不要紧了  燦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇已经由我小卷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇…蛇已经不在了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是毒蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有蛇吗  小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  是条又脏又有毒的蛇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么贝壳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗  海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.45,0:09:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这贝壳里喷出的水是无限的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你尝尝超高压喷射的水弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷  你在射哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒蛇一激动就十分凶狠  我不知不觉就开始乱射了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  真是谢谢你啊  小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄  你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才因为激动的毒蛇情况危急  不过已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  那么有件事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是晒得太多的话皮肤就会红肿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我涂点太阳油到背上么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行  行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未成年人的肌肤相亲情景  反对！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  UFO在天上飞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在哪里  UFO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有UFO啊  永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  失礼失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  那卷贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小燦可是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着凡事都来监视一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会做什么亏心的事情啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}Jet ram attack{\r}\N超速攻壳击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看到了片美丽的花田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的贝壳还能靠超高压水流来飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的努力白费啦  海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  怎么可以被这小个子瞧不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这是在玩什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这无谓地强大的气魄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫就这么想摸小姐的身体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这色狼  禽兽  因为这样我才讨厌男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我承认自己并不是一点邪念都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来涂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就该这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燦小姐的背就让我来涂…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷  不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看你都是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要看的说  H
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷  不要太勉强自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用连那种地方都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗  还是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒啊  小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗  是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那里不行～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要怎么涂啊  自己亲口说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷你坏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:24.27,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一七得七  二七十四
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:27.91,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三七二十一  四七二十八
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.77,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五七三十五  六七四十二…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄  快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很快就来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天都要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得跟她说的  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小燦  脚回复原状了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在湿身了以后还不能保持人样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「还不能」？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说变成大人以后就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人  那几岁才算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  大概是18岁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是20岁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那贝壳还能浮水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要浮要沉都自由自在的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有点像米田共呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燦小姐  那边有尼斯湖水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼斯湖水怪  哪里哪里？哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是在濑户内  怎么会有尼斯湖水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷  到处都不见尼斯湖水怪…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄先生嘲笑我的贝壳的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我觉得永澄应该没有恶意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燦小姐的夫婿应该不会说那么过分的话才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我神经太敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次来这招么  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  燦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去看珊瑚礁的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在濑户内珊瑚礁很少见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让永澄先生看看的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  永澄？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好漂亮的珊瑚礁的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:12.42,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(100,0,100,396)}{\t(0,2500,1,\clip(100,0,704,396))}水深45m…水压的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:17.03,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\clip(100,0,100,396)}{\t(0,500,1,\clip(100,0,314,396))}{\t(1500,2500,1,\clip(100,0,704,396))}我…身处危机…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想到人类的抗水压能力这么差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我不好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不明白的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和不能在海里生活的人类在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有不幸的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了永澄先生  也为了燦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也觉得永澄先生和燦小姐并不合适的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我说太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄先生由我来照看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燦小姐请用那边的毛巾擦脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那双腿在陆地上什么都做不到的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那永澄就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的战略吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  发现啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用普通手段了结你的话小姐会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以老大也没对你下手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他血气上头就立刻砍我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  首先让小姐对你产生不信任感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让她知道陆地和海洋生物难以共同生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你将因事故而死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样小姐就不会太伤心  然后就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了避人耳目才带我来无人岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆上生物知道了海洋生物的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一方就要死光光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是自古就有的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道这个规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来救我的是小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小燦叫我去死  我立马去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:16:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我活下去的话  无论如何我也要活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对救命恩人的…男子气概！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了  小姐也自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燦小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有听到全部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是听到了你要把他的死伪装成事故
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燦…燦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做的话  有损濑户内人鱼的名声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燦  燦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷  算我拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么燦小姐要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要生气的话  请尽管生气好了  燦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷是为了我着想才这样做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燦小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起  燦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想道歉还是想干仗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  这样一来今后小卷也不再会暗杀我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄  你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到卷贝的卷也有失手的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  只是我一时手软
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海蟑螂  今天你得感谢小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事情一定要对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是从早上一直考虑的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天就要回埼玉去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假时再见吧…不  下次连休的时候我也会来的  一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你要等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是异地恋也没问题的  说笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你考虑的事情就是那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  对…对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听说么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和永澄你们一起住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:25.08,in_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)}夜桜　背に舞い落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:30.30,in_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)}どこへ行く道か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:37.57,in_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)}親がくれた命ひとつ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:42.78,in_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)}うまく抱いてもやれず
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:50.20,in_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)}泣いてどうなるものでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:25.08,in_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)}夜櫻　飄落於身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:30.30,in_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)}路途前向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:37.57,in_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)}雙親所賜性命僅一條
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:42.78,in_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)}連相擁也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:50.20,in_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)}哭嘆如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为永澄的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做事半途而废的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有损濑户内人鱼的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写是写作「仁侠」  但读作「人鱼」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女子未经世事  请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  但是我们只是中学生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转学也很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那些花瓣每次都是从哪里来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这这这这是怎么一回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小燦她  小燦她说自己身为妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了要跟到埼玉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以从昨天开始您就脾气暴躁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉  老大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话不如我带着炸弹  将海蟑螂炸到血肉横飞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有红色的流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血  血泪？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如此深沉的悲伤  从未见过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小燦决定了的事  小燦决定了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能温暖地守护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大  既然老大这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只能温暖地守护了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}我们能做的  只有守护啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意身体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要离开父母  朋友  和故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该很不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我做到这种地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在还是有点不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假到奶奶家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带了个这么可爱的女孩子回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  夏天的大事件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被政先生夺去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  最让我开心的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能逃脱那两人的魔掌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  不会再有人来妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在埼玉  和小燦的新生活在等着我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的事情  只有守护了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  刚才外面好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  你在说什么啊  小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的一瞬间我感觉到爸爸飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my 燦  你说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃点心么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  记得点心是在包里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人吃巧克力棒有这么稀奇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卷为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了照顾燦小姐起居  我也要去埼玉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊  永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  我满潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.81,0:21:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭开了新生活的帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到今后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得…非常不安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能温暖地守护啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  埼玉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  埼玉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埼玉埼玉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里就按照我的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了  杀手在身旁的生活会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.37,0:23:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是女婿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的儿子现在正处于一个很大很大的岔道口上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别扼杀幼苗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:42.11,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 1,0:23:39.63,0:23:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&\3c&Hffffff&\shad0}{\an8}男人生活不好过
